fanne foxe ( born annabelle battistella   on february 14 , 1936 , in nueve de julio , argentina ) was a stripper best known for being involved in a 1974 sex scandal surrounding arkansas congressman wilbur mills , in what is reputed to be one of the most reported political sex scandals of the 1970s .

